Layout Technique

CSS
class id class{
    propertyvalue;
}
#class id tangae

.CSS
.you style html elements using css by using the following tags:
-id; styles specific element with the id name
-class; groups a styling and associates it with any element falling within the class
-element name; sty;les any element without an id or class

.3 forms of CSS
-internal; CSS is written inside the html file
-external; CSS is written outside the HTML file
-inline; CSS is written using the style attribute inside the html file

......................................................................
Common properties: can be applied to any element
Unique properties: applied to a specific element


Javascript (DOM)

//find elements using DOM. we use:
document.getElementById('id')
document.getElementByTagName('Element')
document.getElementByClassName('Class Name')
document.querySelctoreAll(css selector)

